<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 13–20" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 13 - 20. Brachiacantha hexaspina sp. nov. male 13 Dorsal view 14 Abdomen 15 Tegmen 16 Tegmen lateral view 17 Penis 18 Penis apex 19 Paramere 20 Penis guide. Scale bar: 1 mm, except 15 - 20 0.5 mm" figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures13-20" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520869" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">18</figureCitation>
), basal capsule crested, heavily sclerotized, inner arm of basal capsule perpendicular to penis, long and slender with parallel sides, external arm in the direction of the tube, twice as long as wide, ending in a short projection (Fig. 
